gw.entity

Class IArrayPropertyInfo

  • gw.entity.IArrayPropertyInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEntityPropertyInfo

    public class IArrayPropertyInfo
implements IEntityPropertyInfo
    Marker interface for arrays defined in the datamodel.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      boolean Owned
      true if the owner intrinsic type of this array owns the array elements. Owning an array implies: cascade delete data import and export semantics are different. Import will delete all items and then import data. Export will export items inline of parent. isFieldChanged on array element are different. Child array elements will be cloned with parent if owner = true.
